<!-- ── WHY + PIPELINE ── -->
<section style="background: var(--bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);">
  <div class="why-section">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label">Chapter 1 · Your Foundation</div>
      <h2 class="section-h">Purpose Is<br><em>Your Engine</em></h2>
      <p class="section-body" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Before niches, platforms, or pricing — you need your Why. Money alone won't keep you going through bad launches and self-doubt. The Core Framework uncovers something deeper: a purpose rooted in your own experience.</p>
      <div class="pipeline-table">
        <div class="pt-row">
          <span>Your Pain</span>
          <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
          <span>Your Product</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-row">
          <span class="pt-pain">Financial hardship</span>
          <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
          <span class="pt-product">Budget planner, debt course</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-row">
          <span class="pt-pain">Career failure</span>
          <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
          <span class="pt-product">Resume kit, pivot guide</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-row">
          <span class="pt-pain">Health struggle</span>
          <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
          <span class="pt-product">Meal plan, habit tracker</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-row">
          <span class="pt-pain">Creative block</span>
          <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
          <span class="pt-product">Design templates, workflow system</span>
        </div>
        <div class="pt-row">
          <span class="pt-pain">Entrepreneurial failure</span>
          <span class="pt-arrow">→</span>
          <span class="pt-product">Startup toolkit, automation templates</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="core-framework">
      <div class="cf-title">The Core Framework</div>
      <div class="cf-items">
        <div class="cf-item">
          <div class="cf-num">01</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cf-name">Your Values</div>
            <div class="cf-desc">The non-negotiable principles that guide your life — freedom, creativity, integrity. A business built on your values doesn't feel like work. It becomes magnetic.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cf-item">
          <div class="cf-num">02</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cf-name">Your Pain</div>
            <div class="cf-desc">Every scar you carry is a lesson someone else is desperate to learn. Pain is not something to hide — it's your most powerful qualification. Nobody wants advice from someone who's never struggled.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cf-item">
          <div class="cf-num">03</div>
          <div>
            <div class="cf-name">Your Action</div>
            <div class="cf-desc">Values without action are nice ideas. Pain without action is just suffering. Your Why must be strong enough to make you write when you don't feel creative and market when nothing is working.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="cf-center-label">"I help [who] overcome [what pain] so they can [achieve what outcome] — because I've been there and know the way through."</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── DIGITAL vs PHYSICAL ── -->
<section class="comparison-section">
  <div class="comparison-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Chapter 2 · The Landscape</div>
    <h2 class="section-h">Why Digital Products<br><em>Win Every Time</em></h2>
    <table class="comp-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Factor</th>
          <th>Physical Products</th>
          <th>Digital Products</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
